@di_dot_csharp_mcp_server_HostAddress = http://localhost:8000

### Health Check
GET {{di_dot_csharp_mcp_server_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### MCP Initialize (JSON-RPC)
POST {{di_dot_csharp_mcp_server_HostAddress}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2024-11-05",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": {
      "name": "test-client",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    }
  }
}

###

### MCP List Tools
POST {{di_dot_csharp_mcp_server_HostAddress}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "tools/list",
  "params": {}
}

###

### MCP Call get_metric_definitions
POST {{di_dot_csharp_mcp_server_HostAddress}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "get_metric_definitions",
    "arguments": {
      "subject": "PRACTICE"
    }
  }
}

###
